{
  "stem": "3605.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had one determination before I joined the underground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before-- when I said goodbye to my family and to my friends-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] with a very heavy heart, because I didn't know whether I'm going to ever see them again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the leader from my organization, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Izaak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- the evening when I said goodbye, I said, how will I ever be able to live without my [SPEAKING HEBREW], without my group, and without my family?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said something that stuck with me through life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING HEBREW], which means 'There is nothing so dear and near in life without what and whom life couldn't go on.' So he said, go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, sure enough, I took a permit from that junk dealer for my father, and I was hoping to help him with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the junk dealers could go five kilometers' radius out of the ghetto to collect the junk, and I thought this is going to help him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Those people were my neighbors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew me well, and then we compensated them for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I smuggled in, into the Piotrkow ghetto, all those things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Smuggling in and out, this was taking your life very much in your hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But listen, this was our life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And no other way was there to function.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name in my Aryan paper was Jadwiga Stryjkowska, which was very close to my original name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jadwiga is this J-A-D-W-I-G-A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to call me Jadzia at my home town, and Jadwiga is kind of extended.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Stryjkowska is S-T-R-Y-J-- the J was added, and it sounded a little-- well, Stryjkowska is an Aryan name, too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was S-T-R-Y-J-K-O-W-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
